                <p class="text-1xl text-gray-500 mb-6"><span class="text-black">The Right to Object:</span> You can object to our processing of your personal data in specific cases (e.g., direct marketing).</p>
                <p class="text-1xl text-gray-500 mb-6"><span class="text-black">Rights Related to Automated Decision Making and Profiling:</span> You have the right to transparency regarding any profiling we conduct or any automated decision-making.</p>
